name: ColorSettingsPolicy

properties.description: Turns off color management for documents whose profiles do not match the working space. For imported colors, numeric values override color appearance.
properties.name: COLOR_POLICY_OFF

properties.description: Preserves embedded color profiles in newly opened documents.
properties.name: PRESERVE_EMBEDDED_PROFILES

properties.description: Converts newly opened documents to the current working space. For imported colors, color appearance overrides numeric values.
properties.name: CONVERT_TO_WORKING_SPACE

properties.description: Preserves raw color numbers and ignores embedded color profiles.
properties.name: COMBINATION_OF_PRESERVE_AND_SAFE_CMYK

description: The policy for handling mismatched CMYK configurations.
